query:
SELECT 
            consultant_id, 
            specialty_name,
            territory_name,
            consultant_f_name,
            consultant_l_name
        FROM consultants
        INNER JOIN specialties ON specialties.specialty_id = consultants.specialty_id
        INNER JOIN territories ON territories.territory_id = consultants.territory_id
        ORDER by consultant_id 
        LIMIT $1 OFFSET $2
